        "contents": "[Unit]\nDescription=Set hostname based upon kernel commandline\nConditionKernelCommandLine=hostname\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=k3s.service\n\n[Service]\nExecStart=/bin/bash -c 'hostnamectl set-hostname --static \"$(/opt/bin/k_params hostname)\"'\nTimeoutStartSec=0\nRestart=on-failure\nRestartSec=5s\n",
